    <h1>Remarketing</h1>
    <p class="description">The strategy of showing targeted ads to people who already visited your website or engaged with your content but did not convert. Remarketing ads are <strong>70% more likely to convert than cold display ads</strong> because they reach an audience already familiar with your brand.</p>
